PROMOTION/RELEGATION PLAYOFFS:

Round 1 [Feb 20, 1983]
Fluminense  2-1  Caldense

Round 2 [Feb 25]
Caldense    n/p  Fluminense
  [Fluminense did not show up. FMF, instead of awarding a WO, apparently resolved to
   turn the series into a 2-game playoff, without any tiebreak criteria: a Caldense
   win would force overtime, whatever the score.]

Round 3 [Feb 27]
Caldense    8-0  Fluminense   [at Sete de Setembro]
  [0-0 a.e.t., 4-2 p.k.]

Caldense remain in First Division.


